data.description: This stunning two-story home, built in 2020, exudes pride of ownership. With 4 bedrooms, 2 ½ baths, and a loft, this 3-year-old gem offers 2,357 sqft of pure comfort. The spacious living room and dining room flow into a captivating great room. Here, you'll discover a well-appointed gourmet kitchen with ample espresso-stained wood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, stone countertops, and elegant lighting. The family room is bathed in natural light and features a cozy gas fireplace, all with Laminate wood flooring. The master bedroom boasts a luxurious bath with a standalone tub, a walk-in shower, a vanity Bar, and a generously sized custom-built closet. Plus, the convenience of a second-floor laundry room and a 2-car attached garage. Meticulous attention to detail makes this property a place to call home. conveniently located near freeways, train stations, shopping, dining, parks, and hiking trails.
